attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Gary Greene-G
Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Gary Greene-G

data.description: Stately 2.5 story brick home located in desirable Denver Court--just 2 blocks from the beach! X flood zone! The surrounding neighborhood is family-friendly and well maintained. Large lot boasts mature trees, privacy fence, screened in porch, sprinkler system, and swimming pool/jaccuzzi. House features loads of interior storage space, gorgeous hardwood floors, built in shutters throughout, and solid wood cabinetry with granite countertops in kitchen and primary bath. Owners' suite is expansive with an enormous en suite bath. Kitchen with open concept living and informal dining is ideal for entertaining! This spacious home also includes 2 recently remodeled garage apartments for extended family or rental income! Downstairs unit is rented through Feb @$950/month. Upstairs unit rented through May @$1200/month. Property has 2 grandfathered short term rental permits for garage apartments that will convey with house. Seller previously averaged $4000/month on short term rentals.
